      The module tracks changes made on files in the IDE and provides an 
      UI to view a files previous versions and to eventually revert a file to its older version.
  </p>    
<p>The main features are:</p>
<ul>
    <li> to setup what files and for how long are to be stored</li>
    <li> to overview the stored file versions</li>
