 <answer id="resources-file">  
   Yes. There are two main cases when the Local History creates or modifies files:
   <ol>
       <li>
           to track the changes performed on files in the IDE by copying created, modifed or deleted ones 
           into the local histories storage and storing some additional data describing this changes.
